{
  "texts": [
    "We then generate QA pairs according to the text description for each image.",
    "Eventually, we obtained a new VQA dataset referred to as DAISI-VQA.",
    "Apart from expanding the answer sets for the questions related to action and organ, we add instrument-related questions in DAISI-VQA to introduce a new knowledge domain.",
    "There are 353 surgical images and 545 QA pairs in the new dataset.",
    "We assign around 80% of the data for training and use the rest for testing."
  ]
}